# Taxonomy & analytics labels

## Source of truth

- How to choose slots: `docs/Analytics_Labeling.md`
- Seed / example vocabulary: `docs/Label_Library.md`
- Schema & glossary: `docs/Database_Outline.md` (do not collapse slots)
- Account CRUD / pickers: `src/lib/taxonomy.ts`

## Do not collapse

| Slot | Job |
|------|-----|
| Exercise name | Display / library identity |
| Primary group(s) | Chart noun(s) when tracking (1–N for complexes) |
| Muscle groups | Anatomy rollups |
| Variations | Modifiers / filters (DB: `analytics_tags`) |
| Tool(s) | Equipment (+ global **No Tool**) |
| Session / Block / Sequence labels | Day or nest structure (+ system nulls) |
| Target shape | Which set fields appear (locked atoms) |

Decision rule: the noun for “one Insights number this month” → **Primary Group**. Session intent, nest structure, equipment, and anatomy are **not** PGs.

Optional full catalog: `docs/New_User_Seeds.md` — secondary to Label_Library for day-to-day labeling.
